subject: Computer and Video Games
Suits and Litigation (Civil)
College Athletics
Football (College)
lead_paragraph: The settlement in the suit filed by student-athletes seeking to be paid included the Collegiate Licensing Company, and the court filing came after E.A. Sports announced it would not publish a college football video game in 2014.
